will be exempt from personal income taxes.\r\n4) Impose an immigration moratorium: Immigration is the leading cause of stagnant wages and inflation. A 20 year immigration moratorium will slow down inflation and cause wages to go up. Many young people aren't starting families because they simply can't afford it.", "author": "China4Biden", "created": 1775340352170, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "greatpumpkin", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "COMBATTING DECLINING BIRTH RATES: Instead of increasing H1-B / other Visas, we need to encourage more young people to marry / start families by 1) Ending Alimony 2) Ban non citizens from buying homes 3) Offer tax breaks 4) Impose an immigration moratorium", "last_comment_created": 1775344864255, "content": "<ol>\n<li>Ending Alimony: Most men refuse to get married because of alimony and current divorce laws. Ending alimony will incentivize more men to get married.</li>\n<li>Ban non citizens from buying homes: The housing crisis is caused by foreign private equity groups and H1-B faggots buying all the homes. This has caused home prices to skyrocket making it impossible for new couples to buy homes.</li>\n<li>Offer tax breaks: Families who have four or more children and are not on welfare will be exempt from personal income taxes.</li>\n<li>Impose an immigration moratorium: Immigration is the leading cause of stagnant wages and inflation. A 20 year immigration moratorium will slow down inflation and cause wages to go up. Many young people aren't starting families because they simply can't afford it.</li>\n</ol>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_